name: Universe #276
description: Universe #276 - The arid deserts of Cheinides hosted no life but a few desert plants. 276 felt sad as it gazed upon it but something caught it's attention as it was ready to pass to other universes, a small patch of plants on one of the worlds. As it closed in to examine, it felt a pull so powerful that their merging was inevitable. Now they are together forever in their journey to grow.
